libmicarray (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of libmicarray
  * Multi-microphone array processing for Raspberry Pi
  * Real-time noise reduction using spectral subtraction
  * 3D sound localization with time-of-arrival differences
  * DMA-optimized data transfer for low CPU usage
  * ALSA-based stereo audio output with spatial positioning
  * Serial port and file logging capabilities
  * Comprehensive configuration system
  * Command-line interface with daemon mode
  * Complete test suite

 -- libmicarray Team <maintainer@example.com>  Sat, 28 Dec 2024 23:33:00 +0800
